== OVA ==
OVA動畫是由[[Ufotable|Ufotable]]負責製作，是「{{nihongo|動畫文庫|アニメ文庫}}」企劃第1期的作品，和《[[百合星人奈緒子美眉|百合星人奈緒子美眉]]》、《[[實乃里Scramble!|實乃里Scramble!]]》共同動畫化，為伊藤潤二作品首度改編成動畫。導演平尾隆之<ref>{{cite web |title=伊藤潤二の魚ホラー「ギョ」ufotableがビデオアニメ化 |url=https://natalie.mu/comic/news/46027 |website=Comic Natalie |publisher=[[Natalie_(網站)|Natalie]] |accessdate=2020-07-21 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515031454/https://natalie.mu/comic/news/46027 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，原定為30分的動畫，後片長延長為75分鐘<ref name="OVA-announcement">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-03-02/gyo-horror-manga-by-tomie-junji-ito-gets-anime|title=Gyo Horror Manga by Tomie's Junji Ito Gets Anime|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2011-03-02|accessdate=2014-05-30|archive-date=2011-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110304011827/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-03-02/gyo-horror-manga-by-tomie-junji-ito-gets-anime|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並於2011年10月29日至11月4日舉行放映會<ref name="OVA-initial-JP-date">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-08-23/naoko-san-minori-scramble-gyo-anime-releases-slated|title=Naoko-san, Minori Scramble!, Gyo Anime Releases Slated|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2011-08-23|accessdate=2014-05-30|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220211643/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-08-23/naoko-san-minori-scramble-gyo-anime-releases-slated|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="OVA-final-JP-date">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-10-17/gyo-minori-scramble-naoko-san-anime-delayed-to-february|title=Gyo, Minori Scramble, Naoko-san Anime Delayed to February|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2011-10-17|accessdate=2014-05-30|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035931/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-10-17/gyo-minori-scramble-naoko-san-anime-delayed-to-february|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2012年2月15日正式發售影音產品。

